title: Episode 186: OATMEAL?? (Feat. Jojo Zarur and Kandi Burruss)
itunes:title: Episode 186: OATMEAL?? (Feat. Jojo Zarur and Kandi Burruss)
description:
Stylist Jojo Zarur (Love and Hip Hop Miami) and singer Kandi Burruss (Real Housewives of Atlanta) join the ladies of Lip Service this week and things get awfully weird when discussing the "freakiest" things each have done in the bedroom. The ladies all address fake rumors that were spread about them, being with men who are terrible at oral, and much more. Enjoy!
